    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1955-09-08T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1955-09-08T00:00:00-05:00" n="172"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d172">
                <head>172. Telegram 695 to Geneva<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d172fn1">Source:
                        Department of State, Central Files, 611.93/9–855. Confidential. Drafted by
                        Osborn.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                            when="1955-09-08">September 8, 1955, 5:35 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <pb facs="d172-1" n="1" type="facsimile" xml:id="d172-1"/>
                <p>695. For <persName corresp="#p_JUA_1">Johnson</persName>.</p>
                <p>Re “List of US Armed Forces Personnel Believed Held by the Chinese Communists”,
                    Defense Prisoner Officer advises case summaries therein of Ashley, Ishida,
                    Olsen, Shaddick, and Turner contain classified information. Pouching revised
                    case summaries, to be substituted for originals in your copy of roster. Return
                    original summaries these five cases to Department for destruction.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_HH_1">
                            <hi rend="strong">Hoover</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
